<module>
    <h>luath</h>
    <p><g>luath</g>
        <en>swift, fast</en> is a <a href="?xx=adjectives/simple_adjectives">simple
        adjective</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>dependents</h>
        <section>
            <h>specifier</h>
            <p>
                <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha an cù <m>glé luath</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>The dog is very fast.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
    </section>


    <section>
        <h>uses</h>
        <section>
            <h>predicate</h>
            <p><g>luath</g> can be used as the predicate of the verb <a href="?gd=bi"
                ><g>bi</g></a>.</p>
            <p>Examples with an animate subject – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>A bheil an cù <m>luath</m>?</gd>
                        <tr>Is the dog fast?</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>

        </section>
    </section>

</module>
